Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.00,0:01:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有惡名的海盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.96,0:01:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍的首領是叫朱羅的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.04,0:01:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被毒鏢擊中的劍心和朱羅戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.11,0:01:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而劍心在力量用盡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.45,0:01:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著海盜船的劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣消失在風雨的海裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.32,0:02:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十六話\N閃電的化身\N自豪的謎樣女海盜朱羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆刃刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是很強的毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是  應該是消失的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來千本屋的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被我們連根拔除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來的目標是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找潮見島下手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那島的話可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.89,0:03:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說有很多很好的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.77,0:03:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍什麼時候成為小毛賊了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.80,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒卑鄙者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要從弱者那裏搶奪東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這應該\N是從我父親開始的規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千本屋是從事惡毒的買賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心黑的混蛋  因為打敗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們有相當的積蓄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.89,0:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了下次的戰鬥\N讓我們暫時的鍛練自己的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想看到流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  把他帶來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.04,0:04:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全員把那傢伙刺殺了怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不這樣的話就不能\N心滿意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的話  好像蠻有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈  第一個可以讓我來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先要從哪裏開始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是手？還是腳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是一刀就解決你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你因為殺女人的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以現在被緊止用劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位給我聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙由我來處死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快給我回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.02,0:04:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的話大家可不會服氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.03,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈  這是你對老大的\N我有意見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.87,0:05:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼各位  走吧走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅老大已經這麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就交給他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不滿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼也是以前老大的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.02,0:05:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  沒辦法服氣\N朱羅老大的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猿次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這傢伙的刀拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝  你也回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.87,0:05:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以\N讓其他的傢伙殺了他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不把我殺了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候  你可以殺了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.27,0:06:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你卻故意不刺殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.34,0:06:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是第一次有這種屈侮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再一次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再一次  戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有…有什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…\N我是忽然這麼想到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.03,0:06:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是在這種情況下\N和朱羅小姐見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是以朋友的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會這麼想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小生也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿刀吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我…戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.59,0:07:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經打算不再和\N朱羅小姐戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.06,0:07:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是答謝朱羅小姐\N救了小薰小姐的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的命交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒殺你的心情了  改成明天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巖椎  拜託你把這傢伙帶到那個地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猿次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我監視他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要寸步不離的監視他知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的月亮不是滿月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍微有點遺憾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很認真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐很善良嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.81,0:09:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像很喜歡她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事呢…銀丈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼沒把那傢伙給殺了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你該不會喜歡上那男人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我會喜歡上他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從來沒把自己當成女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.47,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧\N你可是完完全全的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好銀丈  我可是海龍的頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你只是我的手下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚上的事我會忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姑娘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.34,0:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只有你不滿意頭目而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來一下  在千本屋的貨物中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現了有趣的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.46,0:11:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千本屋的貨物中\N有個奇怪的捆包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查看了一下後發現有兩重底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.80,0:11:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從裏面出現了這東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這東西  該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對  沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鴉片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼作絹布的生意\N那只是表面而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.01,0:11:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千本屋與兵衛\N真是不可原諒的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.71,0:11:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從外國船輸入鴉片\N再推銷出…去嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以利用這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那女的推到地獄去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太…太…太遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍這些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候堆積如山的鴉片到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定是在譏笑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.91,0:11:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船被搶走了\N巨萬的財富被搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.58,0:11:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼只有我會遇到這種事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可憐啊  千本屋與兵衛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你  你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.22,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死而沒死的人就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你  你  你們是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要有那種討厭的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是特別來給你報好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好…好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.94,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後  你所需要的鴉片\N由我們來幫你運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.48,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你必須幫我準備東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對  老實一點\N這可是長生的秘訣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千本屋先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.63,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算這樣到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點給我吃完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住宿的人可不能收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.63,0:12:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我的原因劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定沒讓他吃飯吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餓肚子可不能戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.52,0:13:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的話\N如果知道那些傢伙的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就不能動了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果知道所在地的話  那就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.53,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向千本屋或其他的地方借船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出海去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說沒問題的\N劍心不會這麼簡單就死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才去千本屋問海龍的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道從裏面走出誰了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯  是那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.26,0:13:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還用說  當然是跟在後面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.07,0:13:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是大賭注  可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了  我去找小船來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.73,0:14:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是千本屋\N輕而易舉就拿出這些錢來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真該感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是  好東西\N不是只有這些而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.94,0:14:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛搬來的貨物\N全部是國外的槍和炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎  也讓我們看一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要急  現在馬上讓你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太棒了  銀丈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.93,0:14:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備這些的話\N就能輕而易舉的奪取小島了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我們幫他運鴉片的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.93,0:15:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連新的船也要買給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話\N我們就不需要這條破船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅和之前的頭目的船\N我會拒絕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣呢  想要跟我來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  那是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那  朱羅怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.16,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是讓她從\N這世界上消失掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是條大老鼠而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要嚇我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老鼠嗎……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.17,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到能這麼安靜的\N迎接我的最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.04,0:16:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是太幸福了  但願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像有話要對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想…問你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.28,0:16:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣的女人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.22,0:17:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…叫小薰的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要問這個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.86,0:17:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有理由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是想知道而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣的男人\N能不要自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也不會覺得可惜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是怎樣的一個女人呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的…小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了要幫助別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.08,0:17:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以不顧自己危險\N剛強的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.98,0:17:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是心裏卻很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.76,0:17:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來  有一點象朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒問你這事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不會覺得寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都為了父親在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.71,0:18:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐很尊敬你的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這村裏是貧窮的漁村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有父親在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些小孩子  大家都會餓死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.73,0:18:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些小孩子現在是我的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是父親教育出來的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好像都走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了  不快點找到劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜一點  小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那混蛋  已經注意到我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼  注意到我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對  不可大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下…好奇怪的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.36,0:19:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要離開小生的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去查發生了什麼事\N不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.64,0:19:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的夥伴發生了什麼事\N身為頭目的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可太相信那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家並不像朱羅小姐所想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼有深厚情誼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑  你知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海龍是需要我這頭目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不聽人家所說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這個不習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們剛剛的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐  猿次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猿太郎拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到這麼努力著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅  覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月…月鬼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.54,0:21:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常遺憾  掉到這裏的話\N連屍體都會找不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.91,0:21:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想看到她慘兮兮的樣子！

